data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Would you like to enable auto update?

data.name: textBox3.Text
data.value: An XML file containing version information will be placed in a central server location. This button will generate it for you for the currently opened package.

data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: Path to where you will put the resulting XML and the application's executable: Examples: \\server\public\apps\App.cameyo.xml http://www.myserver.com/apps/App.cameyo.xml https://www.myserver.com/apps/App.cameyo.xml

data.name: textBox4.Text
data.value: Please upload the XML and EXE file to the same location on your server, and make sure they have the same name. Example: http://www.myserver.com/apps/App.cameyo.xml http://www.myserver.com/apps/App.cameyo.exe
